# Contracts testing

- Read **[apps/contracts/TESTING.md](apps/contracts/TESTING.md)** before changing `test/` or `src/*.sol` behavior.
- **Chain time:** EIP-712 `timestamp` / permit `deadline` vs `block.timestamp` → `latestBlockTimestamp` in `test/helpers/chainTime.ts`, not wall clock.
- **Viem reads:** `bytes32[]` arg → `read.fn([array])` so viem does not treat array elements as multiple ABI params.
- **Hex:** `bytes32` strings must be valid hex (`0-9a-f` only).
- Never hand-edit `apps/contracts/definitions/` (deploy-generated).
